INSTALLATION
------------

BestBuy_Service_Remix requires no special installation steps;
simply copy the contents of the /lib directory to your PHP include path.

See "CONFIGURING THE INCLUDE PATH" below for more info.

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-------------------

BestBuy_Service_Remix requires PHP 5.1.4 or later and libcurl 7.10.5 or later.

You can find more information about installing curl here:

http://www.php.net/manual/en/curl.installation.php

CONFIGURING THE INCLUDE PATH
----------------------------

To use BestBuy_Service_Remix, your application will need to access the library
classes. Though there are several ways to achieve this, your PHP include_path
needs to contain a path to the classes distributed under the /lib directory.

You can find out more about the PHP include_path configuration directive here:

http://www.php.net/manual/en/ini.core.php#ini.include-path

Instructions on how to change PHP configuration directives can be found here:

http://www.php.net/manual/en/configuration.changes.php
